{
  "kit_version": 1,
  "comment": "Humanoid kit bake manifest — the single source of truth for what the kit contains. Changing this file (or bake.py) is the ONLY sanctioned way the kit changes; the artgen CI workflow re-bakes and compares. Shape names are the stable, forward-only public API consumed by recipes (no-resets law: never rename or remove a shipped shape, only add).",
